53:11.510 --> 53:12.480
What happened?

51:47.780 --> 51:49.620
The right thing?

51:50.510 --> 51:52.650
I used to know right from wrong.

51:54.190 --> 51:56.290
Life used to feel right.

51:58.300 --> 52:01.400
Kato raised me in the mountain village.

52:03.480 --> 52:05.150
That I called home.

52:06.860 --> 52:09.800
But I found the only friend in my life.

52:34.480 --> 52:37.970
Happiness and love was within reach.

52:48.660 --> 52:51.590
But then the dark dream came.

52:55.110 --> 52:58.370
In the dream, I killed him.

52:58.490 --> 53:02.140
Love was gone, replaced by blood.

53:02.770 --> 53:04.360
Saya-sama!

53:05.960 --> 53:10.000
Then I woke up, and it was not a dream.

53:50.770 --> 53:53.780
Please take your father's sword.

53:53.930 --> 53:55.340
I don't understand...

54:00.330 --> 54:02.510
This sword...

54:02.850 --> 54:07.430
has the power to slay demons.

54:07.850 --> 54:11.960
It is a blessing, and a curse.

54:12.660 --> 54:15.110
You still have much to learn...

54:18.330 --> 54:19.670
However...

54:19.670 --> 54:21.430
We have no more time!

54:22.140 --> 54:25.540
The demons have found us!

54:26.030 --> 54:27.440
Kato...

54:28.600 --> 54:29.440
Kato

54:35.380 --> 54:37.130
Wait here...

54:37.130 --> 54:38.920
And don't come out!

54:55.770 --> 54:57.510
I told you not to follow!

54:57.510 --> 54:59.540
But we need to stick together-

54:59.540 --> 55:01.740
We mustn't!

55:02.510 --> 55:03.480
Kato...

55:03.480 --> 55:07.590
There is no need, I must go alone.

55:08.800 --> 55:10.320
You...

55:10.970 --> 55:13.120
Just what are you planning?

55:18.950 --> 55:22.060
I must complete my mission.

55:22.360 --> 55:24.710
You can't, Kato!

55:25.130 --> 55:28.130
You cannot face the demons yet.

55:28.130 --> 55:30.240
It is my task for now.

55:30.240 --> 55:32.870
Now, go!

22:34.870 --> 22:36.610
Oh I'm very sorry, I didn't notice...

22:36.610 --> 22:40.840
It's been 20 years since we've had people visit, but I hope you'll enjoy your stay.

22:41.210 --> 22:44.980
I also noticed, you won't be needing any help with luggage?

22:46.080 --> 22:49.860
Observant and caring, your wife is a lucky lady.

22:50.770 --> 22:51.610
Yes.

22:51.930 --> 22:53.380
As long you think so.

22:53.950 --> 22:56.640
Shin, my daughter is preparing dinner.

22:56.770 --> 22:59.250
It will be ready soon in the dining room.

23:01.000 --> 23:02.190
I can't believe that!

23:12.250 --> 23:13.340
Sorry!
Why are you still standing there?!

23:27.920 --> 23:30.810
Come out and play my children.

23:30.810 --> 23:33.360
The feeding season has begun.

